channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/D76S5KB.png[/img] [URL=http://"hades718.com/"][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/ApJjzEZ.png[/img][/URL][URL=http://"hades718.com/forums/"][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/oUqzMJH.png[/img][/URL][URL=https://www.dropbox.com/s/bvkttshwzmurnad/Hades%201.2.jar?dl=1"][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/bt8hdYH.png[/img][/URL]
Home- http://www.hades718.com/ Forums - http://hades718.com/forums/ Play Now - https://www.dropbox.com/s/5qjhopsjphk69ea/Hades%201.3.jar?dl=1
What is Hades? Hades is a community driven RSPS striving for fun and entertainment all around, we do not care about profits or investment. We have poured our money into it and gotten some in return which gets poured straight back into the server to add new features, models and much more. We are currently in beta on a road of development and testing, the server is new and so are the features. We're adding lots and lots each day and we'd like you to come and watch Hades grow and develop with a dedicated staff team working around the clock to make the experience all that much better
[B]Starter[/B] Regular - Play what you're used to Ironman - Play the Ironman, Cannot trade or use most stores Hardcore Ironman - With limited amount of lives and no access to stores and more, How will you become legend?
[B]Real RS3 120 Master Capes[/B] If you're like us and absolutely love the RS3 Master Capes, Come check them out.
[B]Boss Pets[/B] Receive mini versions of bosses as your faithful companion from fighting a number of bosses, soon all!
[B]Custom Mini-quest coming this Christmas![/B] Celebrate the Christmas holidays with Hades with a unique and brand new custom mini-quest complete with rewards and more!
[B]Custom Bosses[/B] Battle versus the Elder Wyrms complete with custom and unique phases and more to come!
[B]Fully Functional Client Zooming[/B] Can't see? Shift+Scroll wheel to zoom in or out! Just like RS3
[B]Old and New Items Looks[/B] Simply switch between new and old item look with ::switchitemslook
[B]Bossing/PVM[/B] Difficult and challenging bosses such as Nex, Vorago, Darious and more!
[B]Fully working God Wars Dungeon[/B] Brave the God Wars Dungeons and get yourself some loot! KC Needed
[B]Lending System[/B] Lend your friends gear! Works perfectly
[B]Real Dungeoneering is coming very soon[/B] We currently have a placeholder system that is still fun and working fully
[B]Toolbelt[/B] Never worry about forgetting a tool again with a fully working Toolbelt system
[B]Money pouch[/B] Keep your valuable cash safely in your Money Pouch, works perfectly
[B]Lodestone Network[/B] Use the infamous lodestones to travel freely around Hades, useful for clue scrolls and much more
[B]Summoning[/B] Includes most Familiars, works great
[B]Mini-games[/B] Dominion Tower, Pest Control, Soul Wars and much more!
[B]Completionist/Trimmed Cape[/B] Score off those requirements and earn yourself a Completionist cape!
[B]Highscores[/B] Compete with our most dedicated players on our Highscores!
[b]Automated Voting and Donating![/b] Don't wait around for your spoils claim them immediately
[B]Customs[/B] Off-hand Drygores, Chaotic Claws, T90, Ports and much more
[B]Squeal of Fortune[/B] Earn yourself 2 Spins per day and more for achieving in Hades, such as a 99 etc
[B]Grand Exchange[/B] Sell and buy your items through the Grand Exchange
[b]Hades is in constant development with new features added daily! [/b]
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/GfbdQIK.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/A69R0eF.jpg[/img]
[SIZE=3][B]And much more! Come and join our small dedicated community and watch Hades grow! The Hades Staff team listens to all feedback and suggestions no matter how little or small, if you'd like to see a feature added to Hades, then post it on the forums! It will be reviewed and you may just see that feature enter the server. The Community here at Hades dictates what updates and fixes they would like! Don't hesitate. Hades awaits.[/B][/CENTER]
